# Concept: functions and return
# A function groups steps under a name so you can reuse them.
# Run it with: atena run 07-functions.atena

# Define a function that doubles a number
function double(n)
    return n * 2

# Call the function and show the result
result = double(5)
show "Double of 5 is: " + result

# Call it again with a different value
show "Double of 12 is: " + double(12)
